title: Zeit Like You're Running Out of Time 7/10: Will & Jada, Goya, Robert Deniro, Greyound

On this edition of Zeit Like You're Running Out of Time Jack and Miles discuss Will & Jada's 'Red Table Talk', the head of Goya praising Trump and the emerging Goya Boycott, Robert DeNiro' lawyers claim Covid has made it hard for him to make money, and Tom Hanks has a new project called "Grey Hound"
